        "collapsible_tab_7jVtEQ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "style": "with-border",
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "SUBSCRIPTION & ACCESS",
            "content": "<p>Your purchase includes one year of both Arccos subscriptions — Game Tracking and Smart Laser — giving you full access to Strokes Gained, AI Strategy, \"Plays Like\" distances, live weather adjustments, Green Maps, and more. Works with or without Smart Sensors.<br/><br/>After your first year, both subscriptions renew together at $299.99/year (bundle savings of $100/yr).</p>",
            "page": "",
            "liquid": "",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_yyKcez": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "style": "with-border",
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "DO I NEED SENSORS ON MY CLUBS?",
            "content": "<p>No. Arccos Air tracks your game automatically without any sensors on your clubs. Every shot is detected by the wearable. Just play. You get full access to Strokes Gained, AI Strategy, Green Maps, and scoring insights. For the deepest club-level insights, you can add Smart Sensors at any time — but they're completely optional.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "liquid": "",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_JX3AC4": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "style": "with-border",
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "DO I NEED TO CARRY MY PHONE?",
            "content": "<p>No! That's one of the biggest differences with Arccos Air. The wearable replaces the need for your phone or an Apple Watch on the course. Slip the AI wearable in your pocket, or clip it on your belt, and play. Your shot data syncs to the app after your round or whenever you're back in range.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "liquid": "",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_7yCLEt": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "style": "with-border",
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "HOW DOES THE SMART LASER WORK WITH ARCCOS AIR?",
            "content": "<p>They work together automatically. When you laser the flag, Smart Laser sets your pin location. Arccos Air tracks every shot in the background. After your round, it all lives in one place — distances, Strokes Gained, AI Strategy, and Green Maps.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "liquid": "",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_wxHL4F": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "style": "with-border",
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "WHAT IS \"PLAYS LIKE\" DISTANCE?",
            "content": "<p>It's the distance that actually matters for club selection. Unlike slope-only rangefinders — which account for just 19% of distance adjustments — Smart Laser factors in slope plus live weather conditions including wind, temperature, and humidity. You get the number that reflects real playing conditions, not just slope-adjusted yardage.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "liquid": "",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_c8cn3p": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "style": "with-border",
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "DOES THIS WORK WITH ANDROID?",
            "content": "<p>The Smart Laser Rangefinder is fully compatible with Android.<br/><br/>At launch, sensorless tracking with Arccos Air requires an iPhone. Android support is coming. In the meantime, Android users can pair Arccos Air with Smart Sensors for full game tracking.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "liquid": "",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
