          "settings": {
            "style": "with-border",
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "ALREADY AN ARCCOS MEMBER?",
            "content": "<p>Arccos Air includes your first year of game-tracking membership. If you already have an active membership, you may want to visit our <a href=\"/products/link-pro\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Arccos Link Pro\"><strong>Air (Hardware Only)</strong></a> product page, which is designed specifically for existing members and is available at a discounted rate.</p>",
